---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="bg-background min-h-screen">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-foreground mb-8 text-4xl font-bold">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-foreground/70 mb-8">Last updated: February 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg text-foreground/90 max-w-none space-y-6">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using OpenFeeds ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of
            Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p>
            OpenFeeds is an open-source RSS feed reader that allows you to subscribe to and read
            content from various sources. The Service is provided "as is" and may be self-hosted or
            used via our hosted platform.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">3. User Accounts</h2>
          <p>
            To use certain features of the Service, you may need to create an account. You are
            responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all
            activities that occur under your account.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">4. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p>You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="ml-6 mt-2 list-disc space-y-2">
            <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to the Service or its systems</li>
            <li>Interfere with or disrupt the Service or servers</li>
            <li>Upload or transmit malicious code or content</li>
            <li>Use the Service to harass, abuse, or harm others</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">5. Content</h2>
          <p>
            The Service aggregates content from third-party sources (RSS feeds). We do not own or
            control this content and are not responsible for its accuracy, legality, or
            appropriateness. You are responsible for the feeds you choose to subscribe to.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">6. Open Source</h2>
          <p>
            OpenFeeds is open-source software. The source code is available under the terms
            specified in our repository. This Terms of Service governs your use of our hosted
            service, not the underlying software.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR
            IMPLIED. WE DO NOT GUARANTEE THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, SECURE, OR
            ERROR-FREE.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, WE SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT,
            INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES ARISING FROM YOUR USE OF THE
            SERVICE.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">9. Termination</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to the Service at any time,
            with or without cause or notice. You may also terminate your account at any time by
            contacting us.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may modify these Terms at any time. We will notify users of significant changes. Your
            continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">11. Free and Paid Plans</h2>
          <p>
            The Service offers both free and paid subscription plans. Paid plans are billed in
            advance on a recurring basis. All fees are non-refundable except as required by
            applicable law or at our discretion.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We may change pricing with at least 30 days notice. Price changes will apply to your
            next billing cycle after the notice period.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">12. Refunds</h2>
          <p>
            Refunds are handled on a case-by-case basis at our discretion. To request a refund,
            contact{' '}
            <a href="mailto:contact@openfeeds.app" class="text-accent hover:underline">
              contact@openfeeds.app
            </a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">13. Subscription Cancellation</h2>
          <p>
            You may cancel your paid subscription at any time through your account settings.
            Cancellation takes effect at the end of your current billing period. No partial refunds
            for unused time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">14. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about these Terms, please contact us at{' '}
            <a href="mailto:contact@openfeeds.app" class="text-accent hover:underline">
              contact@openfeeds.app
            </a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 border-t border-foreground/20 pt-8">
        <a href="/" class="text-accent hover:underline">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
